review_blob: Oh my what a brew, Full Head and lots of aroma. Very strong almost....No deceptively strong. This beer will sneak up on you. Its so smooth and the flavors speak of strong caramels. like a perfect Merlot this beer \has flavors of grapes and earthy tones that make you wish you had another chillin in the frig. The color is a deep rich brown to auburn. Pair this beer with a great steak and you will be in heaven.
beer_name: Gouden Carolus Cuvee Van De Keizer Blauw/Blue
